Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:16.26,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:19.30,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:24.44,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I turn my back on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.14,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:33.54,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.35,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Shadows on back streets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.09,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Hands of a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:49.58,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Repaint the time that has been stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:57.30,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Extended hands, puzzle pieces that don't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:06.24,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two reunite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.55,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Something that has been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:18.82,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Recover the last piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:24.66,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's start walking
