Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:45.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought my project was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did I make a mistake?\NWhat did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, I'm gonna look at your script.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me as much as you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ha! What, you're going on a date again\nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to toss it into the game program\nand put it into a game format!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the script's not finished at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:26.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Either way, you can't finish it before\nthe Comic Stall anyway, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:32.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, for this time, I'll just make it a sample and\ncode in only the best parts of the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:39.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't necessarily promise that\NI'd put out a finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the people in my class say anything,\NI'll tell them the truth:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:46.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The reason is that Sato fell behind on his script."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's pretty much because you're all gaga over a girl\nthat things turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you'd been seriously working, by now we'd have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, sounds sort of like someone else I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:02:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HCFCECC&\shad0\bord0\pos(324,94)}Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For now, we've reached a stopping point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's at least have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cheers.\NCheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're busy at work, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Things will settle down by the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't have to cancel our\nlong-awaited trip or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a promise I made to you, Hitomi,\nand that's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it me that's important? Or is it the promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:10.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd really like to walk you up to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going back to the office\nto keep working, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good night, Hitomi.
