Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is Hana-hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:16.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I fought with my boyfriend again today,\nat the grungy yakitori place we always go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:24.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I said, "What if I got a real job?"\NHe flipped out and got violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He hit me all over; I'm still sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HDFDCD7&\shad0\bord0\frz4.939\fscx168.75\fscy191.25\pos(181,30)}Comment
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of taking part in the off meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder why, when I think of a troubled person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato comes to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you read it, Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:03.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm doing delicate work here, so don't\nbother me with pointless stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He made so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are these really gonna sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ms. Kashiwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What on earth is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At our recent meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you said if we have any proposals for how to\nserve citizens, you would actively accept them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I organized my ideas into a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H404040&\shad0\bord0\fscx38.75\fscy53.75\frz0.829\pos(212,129)}Proposal for lmplementing Connectedness Welfare Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no need to take things this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we actually started these sorts of services,\nthink what it would cost in time and personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't think it would put a strain on other duties\nthat need to be done in the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I accounted for that in the proposal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just armchair theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:02.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't understand the first thing\nabout being a public servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shred this immediately, before any\ndepartment heads get a look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you have the time to write this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:11.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,why not double-check the electoral register?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I double-checked it last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then triple-check it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:26.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's so uppity just 'cause she's a little pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The world's not that forgiving a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ms. Kashiwa, don't let this kind of\nthing break your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:37.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm always on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're on vacation starting tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:42.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If so, I'll check the register for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found a good organ-stew restaurant in Kouenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you like, I could buy you dinner sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:51.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you tell me when would be good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H9D9091&\3c&HFFFAFF&\shad0\frz32.28\pos(135,79)}Akira Jogasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H9D9091&\3c&HFFFAFF&\shad0\frz32.28\pos(121,164)}Subject:    "Sorry"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H9D9091&\3c&HFFFAFF&\shad0\frz32.28\pos(193,229)}How are you? About our trip,\Ndue to some unexpected trouble\Nit looks like I'm not going to be\Nable to go. Sorry... I promise I'll\Nmake it up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...unexpected trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until we resolve this, there's no way\NI can get away from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, it wasn't an important promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is precious,\nso why don't you go, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no point going by myself.\NI'll cancel the hotel reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:22.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I swear I'll make up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're still working, right? Do your best, Jogasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:57.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yume to Inbou no\NDreams and Conspiracies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yume to Inbou\NDreams and Conspiracies...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:05.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, a conspiracy did exist after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, why are you so slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:21.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're working at less than half my pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your machine's write speed is\nmore than double mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H0E0E0E&\shad0\frz223.564\3c&H9D9D9D&\move(221,35,286,120,0,509)}Off meeting notice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H0E0E0E&\shad0\frz223.564\3c&H9D9D9D&\move(93,61,168,142,9,509)}"The Island Nearest to Paradise" Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H0E0E0E&\shad0\frz223.564\3c&H9D9D9D&\move(3,-4,80,78,9,509)}August 11, 2006, 11:00 am
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H684F4B&\3c&H170703&\shad0\frz326.757\frx22\fry52\pos(263,154)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare oversleep tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know it's only a club thing,\nbut I want to get in by 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Also, I'll give you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is your copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFF4FD&\3c&HDDB4B7&\shad0\frz82.322\fscx85\fscy75\pos(154,113)}She'll always come back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFF4FD&\3c&HDDB4B7&\shad0\fscx85\fscy75\frz98.299\move(183,140,124,159)\t(\fscx122.5\fscy128.75)}She'll always come back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, this is the game I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:13.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like it's finished;\NI've got this halfway kind of feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I really become a game creator\nby making something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've finally escaped from being hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I owe it all to your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:37.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, Senpai, aren't you hot in that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:40.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't relax your guard, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:44.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a huge conspiracy on a worldwide scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Promoting rapid global warming,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they'll increase atmospheric CO2 levels\nand bring on an ice age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:07.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen! I'm sure you can hear the\nfootsteps of that winter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's calling me this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It couldn't be her, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:32.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C6C6A&\bord0\shad0\frz4.91\move(359,243,247,241,0,3712)}Hitomi Kashiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C6C6A&\bord0\shad0\frz4.91\move(345,243,247,241,9,3262)}Hitomi Kashiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C6C6A&\bord0\shad0\frz4.91\move(316,242,247,241,8,2302)}Hitomi Kashiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C6C6A&\bord0\shad0\frz4.91\move(287,242,247,241,7,1342)}Hitomi Kashiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C6C6A&\bord0\shad0\frz4.91\move(258,241,247,241,6,382)}Hitomi Kashiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S... Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai! It's me, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She went to the trouble of calling me and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Idiot! I'm an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally got through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai, it's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course, did you forget my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you been shut in so long you're losing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you calling about at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:27.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NLet's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:28.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your apartment is near the Mita green belt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could you give me your address?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFEE&\shad0\bord0\frz14.252\fscx77.5\fscy82.5\pos(132,74)}Kanagawa Prefecture > Kawasaki City > Tama Ward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:35.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFE7&\bord0\shad0\frz14.534\pos(137,150)}Ikuta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\frz14.534\pos(137,150)\c&H54431B&}Ikuta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFE7&\bord0\shad0\frz14.534\pos(165,189)}Kuriya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFE7&\bord0\shad0\frz14.534\pos(189,226)}Yadogahara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFE7&\shad0\frz14.534\3c&HFEAC22&\pos(302,31)}First Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFE7&\3c&HFEAC22&\shad0\frz14.534\pos(322,119)}Show Map
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFDB&\shad0\3c&HFFBA39&\frz12.908\pos(327,60)}SET
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFEE&\shad0\frz14.252\fscx77.5\fscy82.5\3c&H7B5634&\pos(125,71)}Kawasaki City > Tama Ward > lkuta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, got it. I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's "shortly" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She can't be thinking of drinking at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl is always sudden about things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S... Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:19.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She drove here?! How does she plan to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was quick, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I bought both drinks and snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is fun-fun-fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! You'll wake the neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai, you haven't already been\ndrinking, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heaven forbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:43.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pure and proper public servants\nnever drive under the influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's surprisingly clean,\nconsidering you're a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:59.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I figured you'd definitely spend some time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doing this takes me back to our high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It does, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right! I also bought some cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been awhile. Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course you won't play.\NWe're not in high school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:27.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is Senpai, who's always had conspiracy-mania,\nin such a good mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen her so cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait; I have, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:44.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was when I was in my second year of high school,\nat the close of the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found you, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't be skipping out on things up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's drink. This is from what our class didn't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:10.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H7B594A&\3c&H3E1F1B&\shad0\pos(197,37)\frz348.338\frx18\fry18}Culture Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My last culture festival in high school\nis over now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, I throw myself headlong\ntowards entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need for the long face.\NI'll show my face in the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad for you playing cards all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:33.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That short-haired loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:36.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The former captain of the basketball team...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:42.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes ago, we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was careless too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was dating that guy for two years and didn't\nsee through to what he really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now I'm cut off from that dirtbag,\nand I can concentrate on my exam studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I can go to college in Tokyo\nwithout anything holding me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a stroke of good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:23.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I probably knew what I should\nhave done at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but in the end I wasn't able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That night was a crossroads in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had roused my courage and stepped forward,\nshe and I could have become...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:47.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And maybe I wouldn't have shut myself off like this.\NI could have led a respectable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:52.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This very moment may be another\nchance to start over in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never drunk this much before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've seen a lot of my miserable side\nfrom way back, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:15.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, I just want to show that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:25.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was right. This girl's probably going\nto start crying pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:34.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the time for me to gently comfort her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then with our mutual love as a support,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:52.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say goodbye to this cursed hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:56.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai! Are you going to sleep there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came today to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've decided to take part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H212121&\bord0\shad0\fscx257.5\fscy265\frz345.302\pos(232,117)}OFF Meeting notice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:33.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no other means of escaping from the evil\nhands of the conspiracy that enfolds the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:37.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was saying something about\N"summer vacation."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B5455&\shad0\3c&HF3FFFF&\frz312.533\frx40\fry36\pos(148,167)}Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B5455&\shad0\3c&HF3FFFF&\frz312.533\frx40\fry36\pos(151,209)}First let me apologize, I'm sorry, Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B5455&\shad0\3c&HF3FFFF&\frz312.533\frx40\fry36\pos(136,254)}Summer Comic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFF7FC&\3c&HEBB6BB&\shad0\frz320.769\fscx86.25\fscy80\pos(147,178)}She'll always come back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:02.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gal game world that's become so stale,\NI'll show you a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:32.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right, I crashed his place last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and then I must have passed out right where I sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More importantly, let's hurry up and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:53.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something painful happened,\nand you want to escape, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go with you, wherever you want to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even if it's to Paradise or the far reaches of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, he saw this, huh? Now he wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You really will?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm hikikomori anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:20.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so it's a good opportunity to say goodbye\nto the cursed life I've been leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:26.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's more, if I'm with you,\NI'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be like that, Senpai. What are you crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S... Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato! Where are you going? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My life as a hikikomori is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll start a new life with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF3FBEC&\pos(193,91)\shad0\bord2.3\3c&H000000&\fscx153.75\fscy178.75}Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HC5E1B5&\pos(193,206)\fscx130\fscy163.75\shad0\bord2.3\3c&H000000&}Welcome to the Conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't have any regrets, will you, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:15.60,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa, ababa, dancing baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:23.05,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.56,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:25.99,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,We were all loved equally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.49,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as it's supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.03,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:30.36,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:32.13,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Each destiny takes a different path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:33.43,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's almost cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:35.07,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some can look at other's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.50,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others can't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:37.97,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some get to learn love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:39.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others don't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.04,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:42.47,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.61,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,A baby, a baby human till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:51.58,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Oh, what an adorable baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:54.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"I just want to love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:56.05,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like I planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:57.59,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It worked perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:00.49,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,The baby she is holding is really a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:02.09,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Ababa!" I snicker to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:03.49,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiding in my pretended innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:05.13,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so easy to be a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:06.46,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should be one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.13,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa! Dance, multiply
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:09.27,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,And take it to space!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.03,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:10.80,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Saturn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:11.54,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:12.20,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:13.74,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:14.51,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.20,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:32.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up with that gloomy group?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Hana-Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They intend to end their lives today!
